# Web frontend layout

```
apps/web/src/
  app/                 # Next.js routes only — thin page files that compose features
  components/          # Shared UI primitives (SoftGrain, future design-system pieces)
  features/
    <feature>/
      components/      # Feature UI
      hooks/           # Feature hooks
      lib/             # Feature server helpers (optional)
      index.ts         # Public exports
  services/            # API + domain functions — never call fetch() from components
    api-client.ts      # Shared HTTP helper
    health.ts
    auth.ts
  lib/                 # App-wide constants/utils
```

Rules:
- Pages under `app/` import from `@/features/*` only (no inline fetch).
- HTTP to `apps/api` goes through `@/services/*` via `api-client`.
- Clerk session UI lives in `features/auth`; route constants in `services/auth`.
- New Module 2 knowledge UI → `features/knowledge/` + `services/knowledge.ts`.
